<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>AnyTechPros · Our Services</title>
  <!-- Google Fonts + Bootstrap + Font Awesome -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:ital,opsz,wght@0,14..32,400..700;1,14..32,400..700&family=Zodiak:ital,wght@0,400..700;1,400..700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css" />

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/common/header.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/common/footer.css">
  
  <style>
    /* ----- reset & base ----- */
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      background: #080d1a;
      color: #e8edf5;
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    /* ----- HERO / BANNER - DARK THEME ----- */
    .services-hero {
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #080d1a 0%, #0f1a30 100%);
      padding: 1.8rem 2rem;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 260px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.05);
    }
    .services-hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -40%;
      right: -10%;
      width: 500px;
      height: 500px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);
      border-radius: 50%;
      z-index: 0;
    }
    .services-hero::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -30%;
      left: -5%;
      width: 350px;
      height: 350px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(123, 47, 252, 0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);
      border-radius: 50%;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .services-hero-container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      width: 100%;
      margin: 0 auto;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .hero-image {
      flex: 0 0 180px;
      height: 140px;
      background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.04);
      border-radius: 24px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.08);
      backdrop-filter: blur(2px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 28px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    .hero-image i {
      font-size: 4.2rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d4ff, #7b2ffc);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 4px 12px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2));
    }
    .hero-image:hover {
      background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.08);
      border-color: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.15);
    }

    .hero-content {
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 240px;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .services-hero-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.06);
      backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
      padding: 0.3rem 1.4rem;
      border-radius: 100px;
      margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.08);
    }
    .services-hero-badge i {
      color: #00d4ff;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }
    .services-hero-badge span {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #8aa8c9;
      letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .services-hero-title {
      font-family: 'Zodiak', 'Times New Roman', serif;
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
      line-height: 1.1;
    }
    .services-hero-title span {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d4ff 0%, #7b2ffc 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }
    .services-hero-description {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #8aa8c9;
      line-height: 1.6;
      max-width: 520px;
      font-weight: 400;
      margin: 0;
    }

    /* ----- SERVICES GRID - DARK THEME ----- */
    .services-main {
      padding: 4rem 2rem 5rem 2rem;
      background: linear-gradient(160deg, #080d1a 0%, #0f1a30 100%);
    }
    .services-main-container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .services-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }
    .services-header-tag {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.06);
      padding: 0.4rem 1.4rem;
      border-radius: 100px;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .services-header-tag i {
      color: #00d4ff;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
    }
    .services-header-tag span {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      color: #00d4ff;
    }
    .services-header h2 {
      font-family: 'Zodiak', 'Times New Roman', serif;
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #00d4ff 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .services-header p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #8aa8c9;
      line-height: 1.6;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .services-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 1.8rem;
    }

    .service-card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border-radius: 1.5rem;
      padding: 1.8rem 1.5rem 2rem 1.5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 32px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.05);
      transition: all 0.35s ease;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .service-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      height: 4px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00d4ff, #7b2ffc);
      transform: scaleX(0);
      transition: transform 0.4s ease;
    }
    .service-card:hover::before {
      transform: scaleX(1);
    }
    .service-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-6px);
      box-shadow: 0 24px 44px -16px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.08);
      border-color: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.12);
    }

    /* ---- CARD IMAGE ---- */
    .card-img-wrapper {
      width: 92%;
      height: 180px;
      margin: 0 auto 1.2rem auto;
      border-radius: 16px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.03);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.04);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      position: relative;
    }
    
    .card-img-wrapper img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: contain;
      display: block;
      transition: transform 0.4s ease;
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    .service-card:hover .card-img-wrapper img {
      transform: scale(1.03);
    }

    .service-name {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #e8edf5;
      margin: 0 0 0.4rem 0;
      line-height: 1.3;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 0 0.25rem;
    }
    .service-description {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #8aa8c9;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 0;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 0 0.25rem;
    }

    /* ----- CTA SECTION - DARK THEME ----- */
    .services-cta {
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #080d1a 0%, #0f1a30 100%);
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.05);
    }
    .services-cta-container {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .services-cta h3 {
      font-family: 'Zodiak', 'Times New Roman', serif;
      font-size: 2.4rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #00d4ff 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    .services-cta p {
      color: #8aa8c9;
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
    }
    .btn-cta {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d4ff, #7b2ffc);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 0.9rem 2.8rem;
      border-radius: 50px;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 32px -8px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.25);
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
    .btn-cta:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 44px -10px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.35);
      color: #fff;
    }

    /* ----- RESPONSIVE ----- */
    @media (max-width: 992px) {
      .services-hero { min-height: 220px; padding: 1.5rem 1.5rem; }
      .services-hero-title { font-size: 2.4rem; }
      .hero-image { flex: 0 0 140px; height: 110px; }
      .hero-image i { font-size: 3.4rem; }
      .services-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; }
      .card-img-wrapper { height: 170px; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .services-hero { min-height: auto; padding: 1.8rem 1.2rem; }
      .services-hero-container { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.8rem; }
      .hero-image { flex: 0 0 100%; width: 100%; height: 120px; margin-bottom: 0.2rem; border-radius: 20px; }
      .hero-content { width: 100%; text-align: left; }
      .services-hero-title { font-size: 2.2rem; }
      .services-hero-description { font-size: 0.95rem; max-width: 100%; }
      .services-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1.25rem; }
      .services-header h2 { font-size: 2rem; }
      .service-card { padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem; }
      .card-img-wrapper { height: 200px; width: 90%; }
      .services-cta h3 { font-size: 1.8rem; }
      .services-main { padding: 3rem 1.25rem 3.5rem 1.25rem; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 576px) {
      .services-hero { padding: 1.2rem 1rem; }
      .services-hero-title { font-size: 1.8rem; }
      .hero-image { height: 100px; }
      .hero-image i { font-size: 2.8rem; }
      .services-hero-badge span { font-size: 0.65rem; }
      .services-header h2 { font-size: 1.6rem; }
      .services-header p { font-size: 0.9rem; }
      .service-card { padding: 1.2rem 1rem; }
      .card-img-wrapper { height: 170px; width: 95%; }
      .service-name { font-size: 0.95rem; }
      .service-description { font-size: 0.82rem; }
      .services-cta h3 { font-size: 1.5rem; }
      .btn-cta { padding: 0.7rem 1.8rem; font-size: 0.9rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <%- include("common/header.ejs") %>

<!-- ============================================================
     HERO
     ============================================================ -->
<section class="services-hero">
  <div class="services-hero-container">
    <div class="hero-image">
      <i class="fas fa-handshake"></i>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="services-hero-badge">
        <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
        <span>What We Offer</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="services-hero-title">
        Our <span>Services</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="services-hero-description">
        A comprehensive portfolio spanning government advisory, technology, and business consulting — designed to help you navigate complex challenges and achieve sustainable growth.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============================================================
     SERVICES GRID - 3 CARDS PER ROW
     ============================================================ -->
<section class="services-main">
  <div class="services-main-container">
    <div class="services-header">
      <h2>What We Do</h2>
      <p>End-to-end solutions for government, enterprises, and public sector organizations.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="services-grid">
      <!-- 1 · Government Advisory -->
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="card-img-wrapper">
          <img src="/assist/ v1.jpeg" alt="Government Advisory" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="service-name">Government Advisory &amp; Project Management</h3>
        <p class="service-description">Policy advisory, DPR drafting, procurement strategy,
           and PMU support for government programs. 
           We assist public sector organizations in planning, executing,
            and monitoring projects while ensuring regulatory compliance, 
           operational efficiency, and timely delivery.
            Our expertise helps governments achieve sustainable outcomes 
            through strategic planning, effective governance, and transparent project management.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 2 · Contract Drafting -->
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="card-img-wrapper">
          <img src="/assist/ v2.jpeg" alt="Contract Drafting" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="service-name">Contract Drafting &amp; Management</h3>
        <p class="service-description">End-to-end RFP development, contract structuring,
           SLA governance, and compliance oversight. We help organizations 
           create robust contractual frameworks, manage vendor relationships,
            and mitigate risks through well-defined agreements and effective 
            contract administration. Our approach ensures transparency, 
            regulatory compliance, and successful project execution while
             protecting business interests.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 3 · Cyber Security -->
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="card-img-wrapper">
          <img src="/assist/ v3.jpeg" alt="Cyber Security" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="service-name">Cyber Security Consulting</h3>
        <p class="service-description">Risk assessment, security frameworks, and audit 
          readiness for government IT infrastructure. We help organizations strengthen 
          their cybersecurity posture through security assessments, policy development,
           compliance support, and proactive risk management. Our solutions ensure 
           resilient, secure, and compliant IT environments that protect critical systems, 
           sensitive data, and essential public services.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 4 · HR Consulting -->
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="card-img-wrapper">
          <img src="/assist/ v4.jpeg" alt="HR Consulting" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="service-name">HR Consulting &amp; Workforce Solutions</h3>
        <p class="service-description">Recruitment, talent acquisition, and workforce 
          management for IT, government, and business. We provide end-to-end HR 
          consulting services, including strategic hiring, workforce planning,
           payroll support, employee engagement, and talent development.
            Our solutions help organizations build high-performing teams,
             improve operational efficiency, and align workforce capabilities
              with long-term business objectives.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 5 · Digital Transformation -->
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="card-img-wrapper">
          <img src="/assist/ v5.jpeg" alt="Digital Transformation" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="service-name">Digital Transformation &amp; IT Modernization</h3>
        <p class="service-description">Legacy system modernization, cloud adoption, 
          and enterprise IT transformation. We help organizations modernize legacy applications, 
          optimize business processes,
           and implement scalable digital solutions that improve efficiency,
            agility, and innovation. Our expertise enables seamless cloud migration, 
            technology integration, and future-ready IT ecosystems that support 
            sustainable business growth.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 6 · ERP Implementation -->
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="card-img-wrapper">
          <img src="/assist/ v6.jpeg" alt="ERP Implementation" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="service-name">ERP &amp; Software Implementation</h3>
        <p class="service-description">End-to-end ERP deployment, e-governance platforms,
           and custom software solutions. We deliver seamless ERP implementation, 
           system integration, and customized software tailored to organizational needs,
            ensuring improved operational efficiency, process automation, 
            and data-driven decision-making. Our solutions are designed to enhance productivity,
             scalability, and long-term digital transformation across enterprises and 
             government organizations.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

